## Common E-Commerce Queries

### Available Inventory

```python
available = InventoryItem.quantity_on_hand - InventoryItem.quantity_reserved
stmt = select(InventoryItem).where(
    InventoryItem.variant_id == variant_id,
    (InventoryItem.quantity_on_hand - InventoryItem.quantity_reserved) >= requested_qty,
)
```

### Active Cart

```python
stmt = (
    select(Cart)
    .options(selectinload(Cart.lines))
    .where(
        Cart.status == "active",
        or_(Cart.customer_id == customer_id, Cart.session_token == session_token),
    )
)
```

### Order History

```python
stmt = (
    select(Order)
    .where(Order.customer_id == customer_id)
    .order_by(Order.placed_at.desc())
    .limit(limit)
)
```

