## Error Handling

| Error | Handling |
|-------|----------|
| Unique violation | Map to domain conflict (duplicate SKU) |
| FK violation | Map to not-found or invalid reference |
| Serialization failure | Retry transaction (up to 3 attempts) |
| Deadlock | Retry with backoff |
| Query timeout | Log, return 503, alert |

---

## Testing Queries

- Unit tests mock repositories — no SQL
- Integration tests hit real PostgreSQL (CI container)
- Verify query count in integration tests for N+1 regressions
- Snapshot EXPLAIN plans for critical queries in performance test suite

---

## Anti-Patterns

- Loading entire object graphs with unbounded `selectinload`
- Offset pagination on million-row tables
- Correlated subqueries in hot paths
- String concatenation for SQL
- Business logic in SQL views replacing domain layer
- `ILIKE '%term%'` on unindexed columns at scale
- Holding database connections during Stripe API calls
- SELECT in loops (N+1)

